1. On *pretvara* da je dobar čovek. (He *pretends* to be a good person.)
2. Ona *se pretvara* da je sve u redu. (She *pretends* that everything is fine.)
3. Ti se uvek *pretvaraš* da ne znaš ništa. (You always *act like* you don't know anything.)
4. Kada sam ga pitao, *pretvarao* se da me ne čuje. (When I asked him, he *acted like* he didn't hear me.)
5. *Pretvaranje* ne može da sakrije istinu. (*Pretending* can't hide the truth.)
6. Nemoj da *pretvaraš* da razumeš ako ne razumeš. (Don't *feign* understanding if you don't understand.)
7. Ona *se pretvara* da ne zna da je vidi. (She *acts like* she doesn't see him.)
8. Ne volim kada mi ljudi *pretvaraju* nešto što nije istina. (I don't like it when people *misrepresent* something that isn't true.)
9. On je pravi majstor u *pretvaranju* tuđih ideja u svoje. (He's a real master at *converting* other people's ideas into his own.)
10. *Pretvaranje* je ponekad potrebno da bi se izbegao sukob. (*Pretending* is sometimes necessary to avoid conflict.)